Pareto
method='pareto', param=[shape, scale]
Gaps ~ (Pareto(shape) + 1) × scale. Power-law tail: small shape → very heavy tail with occasional extremely long hiatuses. Mimics patchy carbonate preservation.

ds_par = downsample(series, method='pareto', param=[2, 1], seed=42)

